V072B405   SIS_405   (TL+)  with turbo-LED active high

V072B40G   SIS_40G   Green-PC, Appian ADI2 VL-IDE, (GENOA and FREE)
V072B40Q   SIS_40Q   Green-PC, Promise 20230C, UMC Superio  (JBOND)


